articles.title: Asteroid Impact: ESA's Hera to go on space hunt - HT Tech
articles.description: The European Space Agency-led Hera mission is all about chasing the asteroid moon Dimorphos after the DART spacecraft crash.
articles.content: Do you know what the Hera mission is about? Hera is a space mission by the European Space Agency and it is a part of their Space Safety and Security Program that is set to launch in October, 2024. Th… [+1983 chars]
